%% Architecture diagram for the repository reviewer application
%% Render with Mermaid (flowchart TD layout)

flowchart TD
    style UI fill:#f9f,stroke:#333,stroke-width:1px
    style API fill:#bbf,stroke:#333,stroke-width:1px
    style Reviewer fill:#bfb,stroke:#333,stroke-width:1px
    style Git fill:#ffe,stroke:#333,stroke-width:1px
    style RAG fill:#eef,stroke:#333,stroke-width:1px
    style LLM fill:#fed,stroke:#333,stroke-width:1px

    UI[Browser UI \n(form & results)]
    API[Next.js API Route<br>/api/analyze]
    Reviewer[runRepositoryReview<br>(review pipeline)]
    Git[Git Clone & file reader]
    RAG[RAG retrieval<br>best-practices corpus]
    LLM[OpenRouter / LLM models]

    UI -->|POST repo URL| API
    API -->|invoke| Reviewer
    Reviewer -->|clone repo| Git
    Reviewer -->|gather readme/files| Git
    Reviewer -->|retrieve guidance| RAG
    Reviewer -->|analysis/reflection| LLM
    LLM -->|text output| Reviewer
    Reviewer -->|structured result| API
    API -->|JSON response| UI
